      "content": "why do you think a human committee would be less impartial than the current system? most people in the district are actually pushing for this because they feel the AI hasn't been \"listening\" to the specific needs of the different neighborhoods, especially in the more diverse parts of the city. they're worried the algorithm is just an \"objective\" mask for old-school systematic issues.",
